    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, once per day as an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Immediate-Actions\">immediate action</a>, you can cause your nanites to surge, granting you a bonus equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level on any one d20 roll; this ability must be activated before the roll is made. If you already possess the nanite surge ability from another source (such as from being an android), you can use your nanite surge an additional time per day.</p>\n<p>At 9th level, you can use this ability an additional time per day.</p>"
